Class: StableDiffusionBoxDiffPipeline. It's a pipeline for text-to-image generation using Stable Diffusion with BoxDiff. It provides methods for encoding prompts, latents, performing iterative refinement, attention handling, guidance, safety checking, etc.

Summary: A pipeline that generates images from textual prompts using Stable Diffusion enhanced with BoxDiff, handling encoding, denoising, iterative refinement, safety checking, and optional features like FreeU, VAE slicing/tiling.
